{"id":155980,"date":[{"year":1949,"month":7,"day":17}],"page":"8","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"磁力","column":"","genre":"","count":"550","ytitle":"","mtitle":"诗六首","ftitle":"","authors":["田间"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海和炸弹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国战争犯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老想扔炸弹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他躺在炸弹上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦想把大海炸翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炸弹扔千万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海岂能翻?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站住!战争犯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你想和大海挑战?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站住!战争犯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炸弹是好玩?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗说:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是炸弹能吞大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是大海能吞炸弹!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老板吟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华尔街老板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你竟无酒装醉?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水能说成酒!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酒能说成水?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欺编能说成真理?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真理能说成欺骗?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"投机的买卖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能做成千百回?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要唱投机戏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请随你的意；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只怕你纸老虎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妙戏唱不成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你颈上烂酒瓶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己就打碎!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他虽有护身符"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管他怎么唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的歌早已陈腐；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管他怎么哭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的眼泪已枯；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管他怎么笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的笑一钱不值。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他虽有护身符，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道能遮住臭骨头?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵然插起翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵然他坐在椅子上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把自己插起翅膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他也飞不到天上；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为他臭的慌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毒的慌，一身烂疮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假如他胆敢冒险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冒险往天上飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动者都要站出来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一人一枝枪，一人一枝箭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫他滚下箭的填场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄生虫的丧钟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看寄生虫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是自敲丧钟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他不拿枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但他要打仗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他不做工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但他做子梦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他叫工人死，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人就甘心服从?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄生虫的把戏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已是一文不值；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戏是毫无可看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可听的是他自敲丧钟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏联赞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏联谁敢侵犯?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水吗?水不敢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林的理想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水沉不了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏联谁敢侵犯?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火吗?火不敢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动人民的花果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火烧不烂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏联谁敢侵犯?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀吗?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪吗?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀也不敢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪也不敢；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不待强盗跨进门槛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界上劳动兄弟们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就要在门外抓住他。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送他到无人的高山!"}]}